            <lg type="edition">
<l>peṟiṉeṉṉām peṟṟakkā leṉṉā muṟiṉeṉṉā </l>
<l> muḷḷa muṭaintukkak kāl</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>After (my wife) has died of a broken heart, what good will there be if she is to receive me, has received me, or has even embraced me?</l>
